{"type": "article", "id": 30750, "title": "小熊智能遥控器", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-08T23:00:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160808204922o4x1LVlR7vfIwT3q.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>家里的遥控器太多？这个由 <a href=\"http://mu-design.lu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mu Design</a> 设计的小熊“管家”可以让你轻松实现家庭自动化。有着黑熊外形的 Bearbot 其实是一款智能遥控器，与家电配对后你可以通过内置的 3D 手势控制器通过它进行各种操作。Bearbot 在激活时会时不时变化自己的表情与你互动，可以持续使用 4 个小时，不使用的话它就会进入最长可达一个月的“冬眠期”。由于 Bearbot 的有效距离为 5 米，Mu Design 还专门设计了一个迷你版 Bearbot 作为红外继电器。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/bearbot#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 75 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808211256SXQe5CmRnvO4fw2j.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642857\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808211256Bhf0P2o58e7MbRnL.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.111765\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808211256d7twhrETlFH0uDWi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808211255Z47WfcPN328M1dLv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}